; autolanding info
; aerodrome/poi = type (heli,rwy), direction (n, w, s, e; x for don't care), altitude, runway length in meters (ignored for heli)
; Minecraft coord convention:
; North: Z-
; East: X+
; South: Z+
; West: X-
; Altitude: Y axis
TMU=heli,n,69,0
AGS=heli,n,73,0
BZR=heli,w,69,0
ZTP=heli,s,70,0
KST=heli,w,71,0
FRO=heli,s,73,0
WAU=heli,s,120,0
ARN=heli,s,70,0
